<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.7">
<l>nalameṉa niṉaimi ṉarakaḻun tātē</l>
<l>nilamuṉa miṭantā ṉīṭuṟai kōyiṉ</l>
<l>malamaṟu maticēr māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>valamuṟai yeyti maruvutal valamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Think [it is] good without sinking into hell.</l>
<l>Strength is to come together reaching the seat of strength</l>
<l>in Māliruñcōlai joined by the spotless moon,</l>
<l>the temple, the lasting seat of him who once scooped up the earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
